---
// ─── Footer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
---

<footer id="donate" class="border-t border-white/5 bg-surface-900">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-white/10
                     flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" class="w-full h-full">
              <rect width="40" height="40" rx="8" fill="#1a1a1a"/>
              <text x="50%" y="54%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle"
                    font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="900" font-size="20" fill="white"
                    letter-spacing="-1">LB</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">
            «Little Bit»
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Працюємо, щоб українським гравцям було комфортно грати рідною мовою.
          Кожен переклад — крок уперед.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Навігація</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          <li><a href="#projects" class="text-sm text-surface-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">Проєкти</a></li>
          <li><a href="#progress" class="text-sm text-surface-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">Загальний прогрес</a></li>
          <li><a href="#updates" class="text-sm text-surface-300 hover:text-accent transition-colors">Оновлення</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Support -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Підтримати</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-300 mb-4">
          Ваша підтримка допомагає нам перекладати більше ігор.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          <a
            href="https://send.monobank.ua/jar/3h4akVJRXK"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold
                   bg-[#1d1d1b] hover:bg-[#2a2a28] text-white rounded-xl border border-white/10
                   transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/30"
          >
            <span class="text-lg font-bold leading-none shrink-0">₴</span>
            Монобанка
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://donatello.to/LittleBitUA"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold
                   bg-accent hover:bg-accent-light text-white rounded-xl
                   transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/20"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
            Donatello
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-surface-400">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} «Little Bit». Усі права належать відповідним власникам.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://t.me/LittleBitUA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-surface-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-label="Telegram">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm5.894 8.221l-1.97 9.28c-.145.658-.537.818-1.084.508l-3-2.21-1.446 1.394c-.14.18-.357.295-.6.295-.002 0-.003 0-.005 0l.213-3.054 5.56-5.022c.24-.213-.054-.334-.373-.121l-6.869 4.326-2.96-.924c-.64-.203-.658-.64.135-.954l11.566-4.458c.538-.196 1.006.128.832.941z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://lbklauncher.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-surface-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-label="LBK Launcher">
          <span class="text-base">🇺🇦</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">LBK Launcher</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
